  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU</h1><p><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592370/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1701979110\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592370/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1701979110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592370/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1701979110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Test your deduction skills and your cinema knowledge</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592370/extras/1135167fbc3f77ca51fadc2379642ab2.avif?t=1701979110\" width=600 height=154 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >See plot summary of the movies</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592370/extras/8f8b82487f306345ae802892a193f63f.avif?t=1701979110\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Some filmemojis are hard to guess</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592370/extras/81a777fd770f07f2ce21443584cfd260.avif?t=1701979110\" width=600 height=148 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 100 handcrafted filmemojis of a Oscar winner to guess.<br></li><li> Has at least one film per Oscar's year.<br></li><li> Type the answer with keyboard or click in buttons with mouse.<br></li><li> Plot summary of the movies.<br></li><li> It's pretty hard to guess alone all filmemojis.<br></li><li> Has hidden achievments...</li></ul>",
